data.description: Bright, well designed Pahlisch home (Kodiak Floor Plan) located in Sun Meadows Community.  Main level open floor plan featuring accent lighting, designer archways, open kitchen with maple cabinets, large pantry, gas range, DW, Microwave & Refrigerator Included.   Two covered patios (one off the Dining Area making a great covered patio for year around BBQ).  Kodiak Plan features 2 1/2 Bathrooms, an upstairs laundry,  and 3 Bedrooms (all upstairs).  Upstairs master has ensuite bathroom and walk-in closet.  Closet in 2nd Bedroom has connections for upgraded communications package.  HOA includes community pool and city park.  Front Landscaping is included in monthly HOA dues.  NEW CARPET installed in June, new kitchen sink and upgraded faucet just completed!!  Move-in Ready!~OPEN HOUSE SUN 7/11 10AM-2PM~
